# claude2026-sensory.twlist
#
# Sensory-modality tagging for adjectives and verbs. Lets a grammar
# pick "a sound-related adjective" or "a tactile texture word" instead
# of any adjective. Most words here are common English; the value is
# in the new tag, not the words themselves.

